room_title: Escape room "Plight of the Margo" by ConTRAPtions Escape Rooms in Fort Collins
room_address: 3720 S. College Ave. Suite B Fort Collins, CO 80525
room_description:
Your crew must journey through the stars to find the distressed starship Margo, but you may have gotten more than you bargained for... come find out what!

Two-part room, each part is 90 minutes. Narrative-rich, challenging puzzles, perfect for those who appreciate world-building in an escape room.
